metadata.name: Zombie Musume Meeting
metadata.description:
Suddenly, a zombie pandemic broke out.
Confused, I kept running and when I finally reached the stairs leading to my friends' house, they were there.
---------------------------------------------------------
突如起こったゾンビパンデミック。
混乱しながらも走り続け、ようやく友達の家へと続く階段に辿り着いた時、そこに友人達は居た。
